    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279300/extras/012650c91019c87c877f5de694466dd7.poster.avif?t=1743586862\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279300/extras/012650c91019c87c877f5de694466dd7.webm?t=1743586862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279300/extras/012650c91019c87c877f5de694466dd7.mp4?t=1743586862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>涂鸦寻宝：</strong>万圣节狂欢——万圣节主题冒险，闹鬼的手绘地图以诡异的诡异方式栩栩如生！深入诡异、错综复杂的素描场景，其中充满了等待被发现的隐藏物品。你的任务是什么？揭开并让隐藏在这些令人难以忘怀的美丽涂鸦中的恐怖物体栩栩如生。当你找到隐藏的宝藏时，看着它们神奇地爆发出诡异的发光颜色，将曾经阴暗的草图变成充满活力的万圣节场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279300/extras/af51fe9bbf2b4f19ebc885b96ea5c599.poster.avif?t=1743586862\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279300/extras/af51fe9bbf2b4f19ebc885b96ea5c599.webm?t=1743586862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279300/extras/af51fe9bbf2b4f19ebc885b96ea5c599.mp4?t=1743586862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>万圣节主题手绘地图：</strong>漫步在令人毛骨悚然但又迷人的插图地图中，其中充满了南瓜、鬼魂、蝙蝠和其他万圣节最爱。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>诡异的寻找和发现游戏玩法：</strong>在寻找隐藏在错综复杂的涂鸦中的闹鬼物品时，磨练你的观察技巧。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神奇的着色：</strong>当你发现每个物体时，见证一次惊心动魄的转变，让黑暗和诡异的世界以发光的色彩栩栩如生。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恐怖地点：</strong>参观鬼屋、诡异墓地和幽灵森林，每个地方都提供独特的挑战和惊喜。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>令人毛骨悚然的放松氛围：</strong>享受探索的快感，没有时间限制或惩罚，让您享受轻松而又恐怖的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279300/extras/6c56bfe35d8fd7b997353d9fe34678e5.poster.avif?t=1743586862\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279300/extras/6c56bfe35d8fd7b997353d9fe34678e5.webm?t=1743586862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279300/extras/6c56bfe35d8fd7b997353d9fe34678e5.mp4?t=1743586862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>涂鸦狩猎：</strong>万圣节狂欢为经典的寻找和发现类型提供了有趣、喜庆的转折，将万圣节主题的视觉效果与引人入胜的游戏玩法相结合。无论您是想享受休闲的闹鬼乐趣还是挑战敏锐的眼睛，这个充满涂鸦的万圣节世界都将为所有年龄段的玩家带来迷人而诡异的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279300/extras/ed7d81599725a9cb2eb0206d109ea812.poster.avif?t=1743586862\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279300/extras/ed7d81599725a9cb2eb0206d109ea812.webm?t=1743586862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279300/extras/ed7d81599725a9cb2eb0206d109ea812.mp4?t=1743586862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好揭开闹鬼涂鸦中的魔法和神秘感了吗？今天就开始您的万圣节狂欢吧！</p>",
